query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS activePowerUps (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  userId INT NOT NULL,
  powerUpType VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  expiresAt TIMESTAMP NULL,
  usesRemaining INT DEFAULT 1 NOT NULL,
  activatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);
